79
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:08,310
Solar City owns the solar cells on the roof of my house.

80
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:11,060
They are selling the power to the grid.

81
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:13,660
They are running my meter in reverse.

82
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:20,209
I paid $2,000 up front to have the solar cells managed by Solar City.

83
00:04:20,209 --> 00:04:22,329
And I have a guaranteed electricity price of half

84
00:04:22,329 --> 00:04:23,610
what I was currently paying.

85
00:04:23,610 --> 00:04:25,930
It's an incredible deal.

86
00:04:25,930 --> 00:04:27,610
How is Solar City able to do this thing?

87
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:31,425
They're able to do it because they are packaging the renewable energy they

88
00:04:31,425 --> 00:04:34,240
are getting from solar investments like mine,

89
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:37,287
and they're selling it on an auction to the utilities that

90
00:04:37,287 --> 00:04:39,120
have to have a certain amount of electricity

91
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,492
coming from renewable sources.

92
00:04:40,492 --> 00:04:42,200
